            "inputs": [],
            "outputs": [],
            "properties": {},
            "widgets_values": [
                "# FrameWeaver Music Video Pipeline\n\n## How to use:\n1. Load your music audio into the LoadAudio node\n2. FW_AudioSplitter splits it into 5 × 4s chunks with 8n+1 frame alignment\n3. FW_WhisperTranscriber extracts lyrics from each chunk (or use fallback_words for manual prompting)\n4. The pipe_text feeds into FW_ScenePromptEvolver for auto-prompted scenes\n5. FW_AutoQueue manages multi-chunk generation — enable auto_queue for hands-free runs\n6. Each chunk passes through ColorMatch → FilmGrain → CinematicPolish for consistent cinematic look\n7. FW_SmartAssembler joins all chunks with crossfade transitions and muxes the original audio\n\n**Connect your LTX 2.3 subgraph between FW_ContinuityEncoder and FW_DecodeVideo.**"
            ]
        },
